snippet.title: Zero Below The Sun - Teaser Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Zero Below The Sun is a survival horror game inspired by the classics, with 90's retro aesthetic in full low-res 3D. Developed by Black Curtain Studio. This is the updated teaser trailer.
https://zerobelowthesun.com
